Hello Folks!


Greetings from Project Management Team, CFI!


This is your chance to be part of Project Management Team, CFI. The
technical backbone of the institute that takes care of functioning of all
the clubs and various competition teams in CFI, helping CFI develop leaps
and bounds.This is an opportunity to understand and get a firsthand
experience of how the managerial team of CFI functions.

Current 2nd and 3rd Years are eligible to apply



Responsibilities that we cater to:


    Facilitate functioning of various clubs by coordinating between
   different teams of CFI
    Conducting regular reviews of projects, clubs, and competition teams
    Ensuring that all requirements of projects are provided for to have
   seamless execution
    Selecting new projects, clubs and teams to be started in CFI according
   to their technical, logistical and financial feasibility
    Throttle CFI to the next level by brainstorming and procuring new
   infrastructure and maintaining old one
    Be involved in the managerial team of CFI and draft the future of CFI
   in your own vision

Want to be a part of this journey, just fill this form

